data.title: KISS ME GOOD BYE (ENGLISH VERSION)
meta_keywords: Kiss Me Good Bye (English Version) Angela Aki
Kiss Me Good Bye (English Version) letra
data.meta_description: Angela Aki - Kiss Me Good Bye (English Version) (Letra y canción para escuchar) - You say my love is all you need / To see you through / But I know these words are not quite true / Here is the path you're looking for / An open door /
data.text:
You say my love is all you need

To see you through

But I know these words are not quite true

Here is the path you're looking for

An open door

Leading the worlds you long to explore

Go, if you must move on alone

I'm gonna make it on my own

Kiss me goodbye, love's memory

Follow your heart and find your destiny

Don't shed a tear, for love's mortality

For you put the dream in my reality

As time goes by I know you'll see this is me here

I love you enough to let you go free

Go, I will give you wings to fly

Cast all your fears into the sky

Kiss me goodbye, love's mystery

All of my life, I'll hold you close to me

Don't shed a tear, for love's mortality

For you put the dream in my reality
